import React from 'react';
import {Card, Nav} from 'react-bootstrap';

const MyNav = () => (
    <Card className="pt-25 flex justify-content-end bg-transparent">
        <Card.Header>
            <Nav variant="" defaultActiveKey="#first">
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="#first">Home</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="#link">About</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Link href="#disabled" disabled>
                Classes
                </Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            </Nav>
        </Card.Header>
    </Card>
)

export default MyNav;
